title: 167: The Walmart Haul Episode (Spring '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode (Spring '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are trying 13 food finds, including iced coffee from an unlikely brand, a McCafé Keurig flavor that is SO unique, cinnamon roasted almonds, Cinnamon Toast Crunch Cake Mix, fruit punch flavored Peeps, THE perfect pickle snack, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new find made from mushrooms that you need to try ASAP. IT’S SO GOOD! So what are you waiting for? Push play, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Spring is in the air and it’s the perfect time for a brand new haul from Walmart!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
